1. **`api/`** - Express.js CRUD API (port 3001) + MongoDB
2. **`mcp-server/`** - MCP server (stdio transport) with tools that call the CRUD API
3. **`agent/`** - Express.js server (port 3000) using Anthropic SDK + MCP client, exposes HTTP chat endpoint
4. **`chat-ui/`** - Vue 3 + Vite app (port 5173), Claude-like chat UI

