## IMPORTANT NOTES:
- Use CommonJS (`require`) for the api/ (no "type":"module")
- Use ES modules (`import`) for mcp-server/ and agent/ (they have "type":"module")
- The MCP server is spawned by the agent as a child process via StdioClientTransport - the agent passes `node index.js` command
- Make the chat UI very polished - this is the most important part for the user experience
- All API responses use { success: true/false, data: ..., message: ... } format
- Include proper error handling everywhere

